==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Looking-glass
<hw>Look"ing-glass`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A mirror made
of glass on which has been placed a backing of some reflecting
substance, as quicksilver.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is none so homely but loves a <qex>looking-glass</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lookout</ent>⟦br⟧
